
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Fırlanan Robot</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .robot {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-image: url('https://example.com/robot-image.png'); /* Burada internetdən alınan robot şəklinin URL-i olmalıdır */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .comment {
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="robot"></div>
        <div class="comment">Size nə kömək edə bilərəm?</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
